flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{System Check}
    B -->|Pass| C[Load App Components]
    B -->|Fail| D[Error Handling]
    C --> E[Initialize App]
    E --> F{User Interaction}
    F -->|Yes| G[Process User Input]
    F -->|No| H[Idle State]
    G --> I[Update App State]
    I --> F
    D --> J[Notify User]
    J --> A